longBusinessSummary: Great Bear Resources Ltd. operates as a mineral exploration company in Canada. The company primarily explores for gold. Its flagship property is the Dixie project covering an area of 9,140 hectares located in the Red Lake district of Ontario. The company was formerly known as Great Bear Uranium Corp. and changed its name to Great Bear Resources Ltd. in January 2010. Great Bear Resources Ltd. was incorporated in 2001 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
